  <body>
    <p>
        XeuMeuLeu is an open-source cross-platform C++ stream oriented library on top of <a href="ext:xerces">Apache Xerces</a>
        for manipulating XML and <a href="ext:xalan">Apache Xalan</a> for applying XSL transformations.<br />
    </p>
    <p>
      Please visit the following pages for more information :
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="site:overview">Overview</a> provides a 5 mn introduction</li>
      <li><a href="site:manual">Manual</a> describes all features</li>
      <li><a href="site:patterns">Patterns</a> present solutions to common problems</li>
    </ul>
  </body>
